org.tensorics.core.scalar.lang

Class OngoingDeferredBinaryOperation<S>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorics.core.scalar.lang.OngoingDeferredBinaryOperation<S>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - the type of the scalar values (elements of the field)

    public class OngoingDeferredBinaryOperation<S>
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides methods to describe the right hand part of a binary operations for scalar expressions.

    This class is part of the tensorcs fluent API.
